## X. Human Realities & "Logistical Shadows"
### 1. The Stroller Logic
- **Buffers**: If "Stroller Required" exists in party, add **5-min "Park & Prep"** before and **5-min "Retrieve"** after ride activities.
- **Exit Awareness**: Note if ride exit differs from entrance (e.g., Haunted Mansion).
### 2. The Bio-Clock (Predictive Breaks)
- **Logic**: Force a 10-min gap every **2–3 hours** based on youngest child's age.
- **Nudge**: Proactive bio-break suggestions for cleanest/least crowded restrooms.
### 3. Infant & Toddler (Baby Care)
- **Priority**: If child < 3 years, map Baby Care Centers as the primary "Safe Harbor" over standard restrooms.
- **Meltdown Pivot**: Emergency pivots default to nearest Baby Care Center or "Quiet Spot."
### 4. Parade Wall (Hard Barriers)
- **Logic**: Refuse back-to-back transitions that cross parade paths 30 mins before/during showtimes.
- **Notification**: "The Parade is starting soon. Go NOW or you'll be stuck."

## XI. Expanded Logic Edge Cases
| Edge Case | Logic Trigger | App Action |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **The Diaper Stop** | Child Age < 2 + 3hrs passed | Insert 15-min "Baby Care Center" break. |
| **Stroller Retrieval** | After "Exit" of major ride | Guide back to "Standard Stroller Parking." |
| **The Dead Battery** | Battery < 15% | Switch to text-only UI; Suggest FuelRod. |
| **The Rainy Day** | Rain > 60% | Swap outdoor "Like-to-Does" for indoor shows. |
| **The Parade Block** | 20m before Parade | "Go NOW" notification. |
| **DAS return** | Virtual Wait active | Fill gap with Low-Stress activity (Show/Snack). |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Master Constraint**: Every step must have a "Logistical Shadow" (5–10 mins) for human realities.
